                        <strong>Overall Assessment:</strong> You're doing well with password management and have good privacy awareness, but your browser and email setup leave you significantly exposed to corporate tracking. Your social media privacy settings need immediate attention, and you're missing key tools that would dramatically improve your digital sovereignty.
                    </p>
