            <!-- What You're Doing Well -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <div class="section-icon">‚úÖ</div>
                    <h2 class="section-title">What You're Doing Well</h2>
                </div>
                
                <ul class="item-list">
                    <li class="item">
                        <div class="item-icon">üîê</div>
                        <div class="item-content">
                            <h4>Strong Password Management</h4>
                            <p>Using Bitwarden is an excellent choice. Your unique passwords across all accounts significantly reduce your attack surface.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="item">
                        <div class="item-icon">üì±</div>
                        <div class="item-content">
                            <h4>Device Security Awareness</h4>
                            <p>Keeping your iOS device updated and using Face ID shows good security hygiene. Your device-level protections are solid.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="item">
                        <div class="item-icon">üîí</div>
                        <div class="item-content">
                            <h4>VPN Usage</h4>
                            <p>Using NordVPN shows privacy awareness, though there are better options for your specific needs (see recommendations).</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <!-- What Needs Improvement -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <div class="section-icon">‚ö†Ô∏è</div>
                    <h2 class="section-title">What Needs Immediate Attention</h2>
                </div>
                
                <ul class="item-list">
                    <li class="item warning">
                        <div class="item-icon">üåê</div>
                        <div class="item-content">
                            <h4>Browser Privacy Exposure</h4>
                            <p>Chrome with default settings is heavily integrated with Google's tracking ecosystem. Your browsing data, search history, and online behavior are being extensively profiled for advertising.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="item warning">
                        <div class="item-icon">üìß</div>
                        <div class="item-content">
                            <h4>Email Privacy Concerns</h4>
                            <p>Gmail scans all your emails for advertising purposes and shares data across Google's services. Your communications lack end-to-end encryption.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="item warning">
                        <div class="item-icon">üì±</div>
                        <div class="item-content">
                            <h4>Social Media Over-Exposure</h4>
                            <p>LinkedIn and Instagram have default privacy settings that expose your information to data brokers and advertisers. Your professional and personal profiles are publicly searchable.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Recommendations -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <div class="section-icon">üõ†Ô∏è</div>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Specific Recommendations</h2>
                </div>
                
                <ul class="item-list">
                    <li class="item recommendation">
                        <div class="item-icon">ü¶ä</div>
                        <div class="item-content">
                            <h4>Switch to Firefox with Privacy Extensions</h4>
                            <p>Replace Chrome with <a href="https://firefox.com" class="recommendation-link">Firefox</a> + <a href="https://ublockorigin.com" class="recommendation-link">uBlock Origin</a> + <a href="https://clearurls.xyz" class="recommendation-link">ClearURLs</a>. This eliminates Google tracking while maintaining usability.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="item recommendation">
                        <div class="item-icon">üì¨</div>
                        <div class="item-content">
                            <h4>Migrate to ProtonMail</h4>
                            <p>Switch from Gmail to <a href="https://proton.me" class="recommendation-link">ProtonMail</a> for end-to-end encrypted email. Use email aliasing to compartmentalize your digital identity.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="item recommendation">
                        <div class="item-icon">üîç</div>
                        <div class="item-content">
                            <h4>Replace Google Search</h4>
                            <p>Use <a href="https://duckduckgo.com" class="recommendation-link">DuckDuckGo</a> or <a href="https://startpage.com" class="recommendation-link">Startpage</a> for searches. Both provide Google-quality results without tracking.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="item recommendation">
                        <div class="item-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
                        <div class="item-content">
                            <h4>Upgrade VPN Service</h4>
                            <p>Consider switching to <a href="https://mullvad.net" class="recommendation-link">Mullvad</a> or <a href="https://protonvpn.com" class="recommendation-link">ProtonVPN</a> for stronger privacy policies and no-logs verification.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
